athering on the Day of Resurrection are those of you with the best character. Verily, the most reprehensible of you to me and the furthest from my gathering on\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33908,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/12\/best-servants-always-praise\/","url_meta":{"origin":22627,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: Best servants of Allah always praise Him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Imran ibn Husyan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best servants of Allah on the Day of Resurrection are those who constantly praised Him.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 18\/124 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064f\u0635\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24357,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/02\/shirk-tawhid-idolatry-riya\/","url_meta":{"origin":22627,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Allah does not accept deeds shared with idols","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 2, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019d reported: T